		 <abstract>
			<para>&marble; is a geographical atlas and a virtual desktop globe 
                which lets you quickly explore other places on our home planet.
                You can use Marble to look up places, to easily create maps, 
                measure distances and to retrieve detail information about locations that you have just heard about in the news or on the Internet. The user interface is clean, simple and easy to use.
			</para>
		 </abstract>

		 <keywordset>
			 <keyword>KDE</keyword>
			 <keyword>education</keyword>
			 <keyword>earth</keyword>
			 <keyword>globe</keyword>
			 <keyword>geography</keyword>
