		 <sect1 id="compilation">
			 <title>Compilation and Installation</title>

             <para>
                 Marble can be compiled as a Qt4-only version as well as featuring KDE4 support.
                 To compile Marble with Qt4-only support check out Marble from KDE SVN into ~/marble and just do: <command>cmake -DQTONLY=ON ~/marble</command> and <command>sudo make install</command>. To compile Marble with KDE support check instructions on how to compile KDE applications at <ulink
                     url="http://techbase.kde.org/marble">KDE's TechBase</ulink>.
             </para> 
